item.obo_searchspec:
SELECT fld_name, fld_dbname FROM m_field f
LEFT JOIN m_objfield of
ON of.obf_field_id=f.row_id
WHERE of.row_id IS NULL

item.obf_query:
t.row_id in (
	select ft_rxl_rxm_1 from ft_rxm_link 
	where ft_rxl_rxm_2=[row_id]
	union
	select ft_rxl_rxm_2 from ft_rxm_link 
	where ft_rxl_rxm_1=[row_id]
)

item.dt_desc:
Sets `user`'s password to `userpassword`.

`user` is a used which has the `FT_ADMIN` responsibility. The user & resp are in the `SimFeature` module, and this dataset allows to make its password deterministic.
